1001
00:43:15,767 --> 00:43:17,200
<i> that's how much I love you.</i>

1002
00:43:18,133 --> 00:43:19,900
<i> I'd wait for you.</i>

1003
00:43:19,900 --> 00:43:21,667
<i> I'd never, ever leave you.</i>

1004
00:43:22,267 --> 00:43:23,267
<i> I promise.</i>

1005
00:43:23,300 --> 00:43:28,267
[PENSIVE MUSIC CONTINUES]

1006
00:43:28,267 --> 00:43:31,033
