to trust you again.

1007
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:34,600
I promise.

1008
00:43:35,800 --> 00:43:39,667
I swear I'd do anything
to earn your trust back, Marla.

1009
00:43:40,300 --> 00:43:42,167
