1024
00:45:08,367 --> 00:45:11,667
[CLEAR THROAT]

1025
00:45:19,700 --> 00:45:26,667
[UNSETTLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

1026
00:45:34,267 --> 00:45:35,333
Isobel

1027
