Did you put in
some sleeping pills?

1030
00:45:46,867 --> 00:45:49,133
It‘s not sleeping pills.

1031
00:45:49,133 --> 00:45:51,333
[UNSETTLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

1032
00:45:51,333 --> 00:45:53,367
