1033
00:45:53,367 --> 00:45:55,033
Did you poison me?

1034
00:45:55,033 --> 00:45:56,867
Is this... poison?

1035
00:45:56,867 --> 00:45:57,967
[ISOBEL] Chill!

1036
00:45:57,967 --> 00:46:00,300
I'm not gonna poison you yet.

1037
00:46:00,300 --> 00:46:01,433
[APRIL] Why can't I breathe?

1038
00:46:01,433 --> 00:46:03,300
- It's hot.
- Just kidding. Um...

1039
00:46:03,967 --> 00:46:06,300
[ISOBEL]
It's just a truth serum.

1040
00:46:07,000 --> 00:46:08,267
Truth serum?!

1041
00:46:08,267 --> 00:46:10,867
What is a freaking truth serum,
