1046
00:46:21,833 --> 00:46:23,967
You spiked my drink?!

1047
00:46:23,967 --> 00:46:25,000
Why?

1048
00:46:25,000 --> 00:46:25,967
[MARLA] Actually...

1049
00:46:26,767 --> 00:46:28,133
it was my idea.

1050
00:46:29,033 --> 00:46:30,967
Isobel didn't wanna do this.

1051
00:46:31,367 --> 00:46:32,867
But it had to be done.

1052
00:46:34,067 --> 00:46:36,067
We need to know the truth,
April.

1053
00:46:36,067 --> 00:46:38,400
What are you talking about,
Marla?

1054
00:46:39,400 --> 00:46:41,800
Did you leak our nudes?

1055
00:46:41,800 --> 00:46:44,167
Huh?! Why would I do that?

1056
00:46:44,200 --> 00:46:45,267
Well, why indeed?

1057
00:46:45,267 --> 00:46:46,567
What are you talking about?

1058
00:46:46,567 --> 00:46:48,133
You saw their GC, didn't you?

1059
00:46:48,133 --> 00:46:50,467
You've read
the boys' messages.

1060
00:46:50,467 --> 00:46:52,933
