manipulated those images.

1061
00:46:53,233 --> 00:46:55,500
And why would I do that, Marla?

1062
00:46:55,500 --> 00:46:57,233
[MARLA] Because you're
still mad at me

1063
00:46:57,567 --> 00:47:00,100
