before?

1064
00:47:00,100 --> 00:47:01,500
Are you joking?

1065
00:47:01,500 --> 00:47:03,367
That was history, Marla.

1066
00:47:03,867 --> 00:47:07,200
Besides, you were the ones
who approached me.

1067
00:47:07,200 --> 00:47:10,500
I was minding my own business
when you asked for my help.

