1340
00:59:57,100 --> 00:59:59,600
I don't want us
to be his punching bag, okay?

1341
01:00:00,300 --> 01:00:02,233
I don't want a mediocre life,

1342
01:00:04,600 --> 01:00:06,000
and I can't do all that

1343
01:00:06,000 --> 01:00:08,600
if we will just work in
a fast food restaurant.

1344
01:00:10,267 --> 01:00:11,767
Our expenses would cost more

1345
01:00:11,767 --> 01:00:13,567
than our salary, wouldn't it?

1346
01:00:14,200 --> 01:00:15,700
I hope you know that.

1347
01:00:18,300 --> 01:00:19,667
Don't cry.

1348
01:00:19,667 --> 01:00:21,700
When will this end?

1349
01:00:21,700 --> 01:00:22,900
[SOBS]

1350
01:00:25,367 --> 01:00:26,700
I'm just here, okay?

1351
01:00:28,167 --> 01:00:30,133
I'm so tired, Cole.

1352
01:00:31,033 --> 01:00:32,167
[SOBBING]

1353
01:00:32,967 --> 01:00:34,733
[EXHALES DEEPLY]

1354
01:00:34,733 --> 01:00:35,800
[SNIFFLES]

1355
01:00:35,800 --> 01:00:41,233
[SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES]

1356
01:00:46,067 --> 01:00:47,733
"Marla, are we still good
for tomorrow?

1357
01:00:47,733 --> 01:00:48,833
I'll pick you up.

1358
01:00:48,833 --> 01:00:50,100
So excited to see you."

1359
01:00:52,000 --> 01:00:53,267
"I'm so sorry, Warren.

1360
01:00:53,267 --> 01:00:54,100
I'm sick with the flu.

1361
01:00:54,100 --> 01:00:55,933
I think
I can't make it tomorrow.

1362
01:00:55,933 --> 01:00:57,300
I'm really sorry."

1363
01:00:58,367 --> 01:01:00,100
"I hope you're okay.
Get well soon.

1364
01:01:00,100 --> 01:01:01,167
Let's just reschedule?"

1365
01:01:02,733 --> 01:01:04,633
"Thank you, Warren."

1366
01:01:04,633 --> 01:01:11,367
[PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING]

1367
01:01:13,333 --> 01:01:14,733
Okay, girls.

1368
01:01:15,067 --> 01:01:16,667
Let's get back to business.

1369
01:01:25,167 --> 01:01:28,267
Our next target is

1370
01:01:31,300 --> 01:01:33,233
April Javier.

1371
01:01:33,233 --> 01:01:40,200
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

